items.name: File_Organizer
items.description: Organize your downloads like a pro gamer! This Python script categorizes files into folders (Images, Videos, Games, etc.) based on file types. Utilizes the IGDB API to accurately sort game-related files. Supports a wide range of file extensions for comprehensive organization. Easy setup and usage.
